            <lg xml:id="TK83">
<l>varuviruntu vaikalu mōmpuvāṉ vāḻkkai</l>
<l>paruvantu pāḻpaṭuta liṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The life of one who each day cherishes the guests that come</l>
<l>knows neither suffering nor ruin.</l>
